    * fitness, workout, running</p>
<p>As we can see in this case, there are exceptions like the first sub-cluster.. ( shopping , research). But mostly it works well. </p>
<p>I think all this shows that the clustering algorithm is good, Though the retrieval algorithm is not so precise.</p>
